---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  pageKey="privacy"
  title="Politika privatnosti – BL Prevoz"
  description="Politika privatnosti BL Prevoz platforme. Informacije o korištenju analitike, kolačića i zaštiti vaših podataka."
  canonicalUrl="https://blprevoz.com/privacy/"
>
  <section class="section section--narrow" id="privacy">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section__title" id="privacy-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Politika privatnosti</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Privacy Policy</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="privacy-content">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div data-lang="bhs">
          <h2>Uvod</h2>
          <p>
            Ova politika privatnosti odnosi se na korištenje internet stranice <a href="https://blprevoz.com">blprevoz.com</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz je nezavisna, nekomercijalna platforma za informacije
            o javnom prevozu u Banjoj Luci.
          </p>
          <p>
            Vaša privatnost nam je važna. Ova stranica objašnjava kako koristimo analitiku i kolačiće prilikom
            korištenja ovog sajta.
          </p>

          <h2>Upravljač sajta</h2>
          <p>
            Internet stranicu blprevoz.com vodi BL Prevoz, nezavisna informativna platforma koja nije povezana sa
            zvaničnim institucijama niti prevoznicima.
          </p>

          <h2>Analitika</h2>
          <p>
            Ovaj sajt koristi <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> kako bismo razumjeli na koji način se sajt koristi
            i kako bismo mogli poboljšati korisničko iskustvo.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analitika se aktivira <strong>isključivo nakon vašeg pristanka</strong> putem banera za kolačiće.
          </p>
          <p>Prikupljaju se isključivo agregirani i anonimizovani podaci, kao što su:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Broj posjeta stranicama</li>
            <li>Trajanje posjete</li>
            <li>Tip uređaja i pretraživača</li>
            <li>Država iz koje se pristupa sajtu (bez precizne lokacije)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Ne prikupljamo lične podatke kao što su imena, email adrese, telefonski brojevi niti bilo kakve
            informacije koje mogu direktno identifikovati korisnika.
          </p>
          <p>
            Google Analytics može obrađivati skraćene (anonimizovane) IP adrese u skladu sa svojom politikom privatnosti.
          </p>
          <p>
            Više informacija dostupno je u <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google-ovoj politici privatnosti</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Kolačići</h2>
          <p>Ovaj sajt koristi sljedeće kolačiće i lokalne podatke:</p>
          <p>
            <strong>analytics-consent</strong> (localStorage)<br />
            Čuva vašu odluku o prihvatanju ili odbijanju analitičkih kolačića.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Google Analytics kolačići</strong> (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code>)<br />
            Postavljaju se samo ako prihvatite analitiku. Koriste se za razlikovanje korisnika i sesija u svrhu
            analize korištenja sajta.
          </p>
          <p>
            Svoju odluku možete promijeniti brisanjem podataka pretraživača (localStorage) ili brisanjem kolačića
            za ovaj sajt.
          </p>
          <p>
            Korištenjem banera za kolačiće možete prihvatiti ili odbiti korištenje analitičkih kolačića.
          </p>

          <h2>Prava korisnika</h2>
          <p>Imate pravo da:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>zatražite informacije o obradi podataka</li>
            <li>povučete pristanak za analitičke kolačiće</li>
            <li>zatražite brisanje podataka koji se mogu odnositi na vas</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            S obzirom da ovaj sajt ne prikuplja lične podatke niti koristi korisničke naloge,
            većina ovih prava praktično nije primjenjiva. Pristanak za analitiku možete povući
            brisanjem kolačića za ovaj sajt.
          </p>

          <h2>Zadržavanje podataka</h2>
          <p>
            Analitički podaci čuvaju se u skladu sa podešavanjima zadržavanja podataka u servisu Google Analytics.
            Koriste se isključivo za statističku analizu korištenja sajta.
          </p>

          <h2>Eksterni linkovi</h2>
          <p>
            Ovaj sajt može sadržavati linkove ka eksternim internet stranicama, uključujući prevoznike,
            gradske institucije i aerodromske resurse.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz nije odgovoran za politike privatnosti niti sadržaj eksternih sajtova.
            Preporučujemo da pregledate politike privatnosti tih sajtova zasebno.
          </p>

          <h2>Kontakt</h2>
          <p>
            Za sva pitanja u vezi privatnosti možete nas kontaktirati na
            <a href="mailto:blprevoz@proton.me">blprevoz@proton.me</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Odricanje odgovornosti</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz je nezavisna platforma i nije povezana sa zvaničnim gradskim institucijama niti prevoznicima.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analitički podaci koriste se isključivo za razumijevanje korištenja sajta i unapređenje korisničkog iskustva.
          </p>
          <p>
            Podaci se ne prodaju, ne dijele niti prenose trećim stranama, osim Google Analytics servisu u gore
            opisane svrhe.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- English version -->
        <div data-lang="en" style="display:none">
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            This privacy policy applies to the use of the website <a href="https://blprevoz.com">blprevoz.com</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is an independent, non-commercial platform for
            public transport information in Banja Luka.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your privacy is important to us. This page explains how we use analytics and cookies when using this site.
          </p>

          <h2>Site Operator</h2>
          <p>
            The website blprevoz.com is operated by BL Prevoz, an independent informational platform
            not affiliated with official institutions or transport operators.
          </p>

          <h2>Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            This site uses <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> to understand how the site is used and to improve
            the user experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analytics is activated <strong>only after your consent</strong> via the cookie banner.
          </p>
          <p>Only aggregated and anonymized data is collected, such as:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Page view counts</li>
            <li>Visit duration</li>
            <li>Device and browser type</li>
            <li>Country of access (no precise location)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We do not collect personal data such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any information that
            can directly identify a user.
          </p>
          <p>
            Google Analytics may process shortened (anonymized) IP addresses in accordance with its own privacy policy.
          </p>
          <p>
            More information is available in <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>This site uses the following cookies and local data:</p>
          <p>
            <strong>analytics-consent</strong> (localStorage)<br />
            Stores your decision to accept or decline analytics cookies.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Google Analytics cookies</strong> (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code>)<br />
            Set only if you accept analytics. Used to distinguish users and sessions for site usage analysis.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can change your decision by clearing your browser data (localStorage) or deleting cookies for this site.
          </p>
          <p>
            Using the cookie banner, you can accept or decline the use of analytics cookies.
          </p>

          <h2>User Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>request information about data processing</li>
            <li>withdraw consent for analytics cookies</li>
            <li>request deletion of data that may relate to you</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Since this site does not collect personal data or use user accounts,
            most of these rights are not practically applicable. You can withdraw analytics consent
            by clearing cookies for this site.
          </p>

          <h2>Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Analytics data is stored according to the retention settings configured in Google Analytics.
            It is used solely for statistical analysis of site usage.
          </p>

          <h2>External Links</h2>
          <p>
            This site may contain links to external websites, including transport operators,
            city institutions, and airport-related resources.
          </p>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is not responsible for the privacy policies or content of external websites.
            We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of those sites separately.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any privacy-related questions, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:blprevoz@proton.me">blprevoz@proton.me</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is an independent platform and is not affiliated with official city authorities or transport operators.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analytics data is used solely to understand site usage and improve the user experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Data is not sold, shared, or transferred to third parties, except for the Google Analytics service
            as described above.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
